[Complete prompt with explicit style, lighting, medium, mood]

### Variant 2: Tech-Forward Dynamic
[Complete prompt with different style, lighting, medium, mood]

### Variant 3: Professional Corporate
[Complete prompt with different style, lighting, medium, mood]
```

